title: Naturi Naughton And Omari Hardwick: Power Puzzlers
description: Naturi Naughton and Omari Hardwick reveal what inspires their characters on Starz's Power, then sing the titles to classic 90s R&B hits. This episode originally aired on August 26, 2016.
